---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="homeWhat homeSection">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="homeSectionHeader">
      <span class="homeSectionHeader__sup">What is Rebound?</span>
      <h2>Deliver products people can rely on</h2>
    </header>

    <ul class="homeWhat__list list-reset">
      <li class="homeWhatCard">
        <header class="homeWhatCard__header">
          <h3>System Agnostic</h3>
          <div class="homeWhatCard__icon">
            <Icon name="feather/server" />
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="homeWhatCard__content">
          <p>
            <strong
              >Rebound's toolbox is not bound to a particular system.</strong
            > Whether it's Cloud, On-Premise or "It's complicated", Rebound follows.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="homeWhatCard">
        <header class="homeWhatCard__header">
          <h3>Metrics Driven</h3>
          <div class="homeWhatCard__icon">
            <Icon name="feather/bar-chart" />
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="homeWhatCard__content">
          <p>
            <strong>With knowledge comes wisdom.</strong> Rebound has a mission to
            turn resilience from a perceived cost to a must-have strategic asset.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="homeWhatCard">
        <header class="homeWhatCard__header">
          <h3>Scales With You</h3>
          <div class="homeWhatCard__icon">
            <Icon name="feather/maximize-2" />
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="homeWhatCard__content">
          <p>
            <strong>Grow at your own pace.</strong> Rebound adapts to your journeyâ€”from
            early development to enterprise operations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="homeWhatCard">
        <header class="homeWhatCard__header">
          <h3>No Lock-In</h3>
          <div class="homeWhatCard__icon">
            <Icon name="feather/unlock" />
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="homeWhatCard__content">
          <p>
            <strong>Naturally Open-Source.</strong> Invest safely in the future by
            owning the stack.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="homeWhatCard">
        <header class="homeWhatCard__header">
          <h3>Engineers First</h3>
          <div class="homeWhatCard__icon">
            <Icon name="feather/user" />
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="homeWhatCard__content">
          <p>
            <strong>Useful not painful.</strong>
            Rebound encourages resilience thinking at all stages without being obnoxious.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .homeWhat {
    --what-card-header-background: var(--grey-200);

    background-color: white;

    header {
      h2 {
        br {
          display: none;

          @media (width > 40rem) {
            display: block;
          }
        }
      }
    }
    &__list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-large);

      @media (width > 50rem) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .homeWhatCard {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius-m);
      box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-diffuse);

      &__header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: var(--space-small);

        background-color: var(--what-card-header-background);

        h3 {
          margin-bottom: 0;

          font-size: 2rem;
        }
      }

      &__icon {
        svg {
          height: 2.4rem;
          width: auto;
        }
      }

      &__content {
        padding: var(--space-small);

        p {
          color: var(--text-color-dim);
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
